# Mailmap — normalize attribution for GitHub Contributors sidebar & git shortlog.
# Format: Canonical Name <email> Legacy Name <email>
# Reference: https://git-scm.com/docs/gitmailmap
#
# GitHub applies this at display time (no history rewrite). Co-Authored-By
# trailers from briefly-pushed commits are routed to the project owner.

